<h1>Research Projects</h1>
<ol start="1" type="i">
<li>Coordinator, Strategic Conflict Assessment of Niger Delta Region. Institute for Peace and Conflict Resolution (IPRC), Abuja (Funded by the World Bank, USAID, DFID and FGN).</li>
<li>Research Coordinator, “Warri Crisis Project”, Academic Associates Peace Work (funded by United States Peace Institute), (1999-2000).</li>
<li><b>AFSTRAG</b> (African Strategic and Peace Research Group) Research Networks:
<ol start="1" type="a">      
<li>Peace-Keeping as Conflict Management Strategy (Chad and Liberia).</li>
<li>Nigerian in International Peace-Keeping (Funded by Defence Headquarters).</li>
<li>Ethnicity, Violence and Civil Society in Nigeria, Ford Foundation (1999).</li>
<li>Child Soldiers Project (Liberia and Sierra Leone), Ford Foundation (2000).</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>Member, Research Team on Nigeria in ECOMOG Lessons Learned 	Series, Nigeria Defence Academy Project (2014-2015): 5 Volumes.</li>
<li>Project series on Nigerian Defence Establishment, African Centre for Security Studies, Abuja:
<ul type="square">
<li>Bassey C. and Dokuboh C. Defence Policy of Nigeria (Published 2011)</li>
<li>Bassey C. and Yorom G. The Nigerian Navy and Regional Maritime Challenges (In partnership with the Office of CNS, Defence Headquarters, Abuja).</li>
<li>Bassey C, and Yorom G. Nigerian Air Force and Challenges of Airpower in the 21st Century (In partnership with the Office CAS, Defence Headquarters, Abuja).</li>
<li>Bassey C. and Tar U. The Nigerian Army and the Challenges of Institutional Transformation in the 21st Century.</li>
<li>Bassey, C and Alabi, D, Force, Strategy and War – Reader in Strategic Studies.</li>
</ul>
</li>
